data.eml:eml: Leaf-litter thrips of the genus Psalidothrips (Thysanoptera, Phlaeothripidae) from Australia, with fifteen new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Wang, Jun, Mound, Laurence A., Tree, Desley J.
